

TRIMSIZE

\trimsize{w=W,h=H}

W and H are the dimensions of your book pages. Default w=5.5in,h=8.5in.
	You may specify W and H in units of in or mm. Both must be set.
Width cannot exceed height.


MARGINS

\margins{t=T,o=O,b=B,i=I}

T, O, B, and I are the dimensions of page margins.  Top, ouside, bottom, inside (spine).
Default t=.5in,o=.5in,b=.5in,i=.625in.
	You may specify them in units of in or mm. All four must be set.
In general, I exceeds O by at least 3mm or .125in, to allow for spine binding glue.
